sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Usuario
    participant P as Finance page
    participant A as apiRequest
    participant E as /api/expenses
    participant EI as /api/expenses/[id]
    participant ER as /api/expenses/[id]/restore
    participant SU as serverUtils
    participant DB as Firestore expenses

    U->>P: Abre /finance
    P->>A: GET /expenses?startDate&endDate
    A->>E: fetch /api/expenses
    E->>DB: where isDeleted == false\norderBy date desc\nfiltra start/end si existen
    DB-->>E: documentos expense
    E-->>A: lista serializada
    A-->>P: expenses[]
    P-->>U: render tabla y totales

    U->>P: Crea gasto
    P->>A: POST /expenses
    A->>E: body JSON
    E->>SU: buildExpensePayload()
    SU-->>E: payload validado
    E->>DB: add expense + timestamps + isDeleted=false
    DB-->>E: documento creado
    E-->>A: expense 201
    A-->>P: respuesta creada
    P->>A: GET /expenses
    A->>E: refetch lista
    E->>DB: query vigente
    DB-->>E: lista actualizada
    E-->>P: expenses[]

    U->>P: Edita gasto
    P->>A: PUT /expenses/[id]
    A->>EI: body JSON
    EI->>SU: buildExpensePayload()
    SU-->>EI: payload validado
    EI->>DB: get doc por id
    DB-->>EI: documento existente
    EI->>DB: update payload + updatedAt
    DB-->>EI: documento actualizado
    EI-->>A: expense actualizado
    A-->>P: respuesta actualizada

    U->>P: Envía a papelera
    P->>A: DELETE /expenses/[id]
    A->>EI: delete lógico
    EI->>DB: get doc por id
    DB-->>EI: documento existente
    EI->>DB: update isDeleted=true\ndeletedAt=now\nupdatedAt=now
    DB-->>EI: documento actualizado
    EI-->>P: expense en papelera

    U->>P: Activa vista trash
    P->>A: GET /expenses?includeDeleted=true
    A->>E: fetch trash
    E->>DB: where isDeleted == true
    DB-->>E: documentos en papelera
    E-->>P: expenses[]

    U->>P: Restaura gasto
    P->>A: PATCH /expenses/[id]/restore
    A->>ER: restore
    ER->>DB: get doc por id
    DB-->>ER: documento con isDeleted=true
    ER->>DB: update isDeleted=false\ndeletedAt=null\nupdatedAt=now
    DB-->>ER: documento restaurado
    ER-->>P: expense restaurado
